Vagrant Puppet

Vagrant Project to help speed up puppet development.

Installation:
NOTE: Right now only supports puppet enterprise master on ubuntu

Download puppet enterprise master tar file for ubuntu from puppetlabs.com and place it in software directory
Similarly download agent tar files on in the same directory


Usage: 
  To deploy and setup puppet master: vagrant up master

  Roadmap:
    To deploy and setup puppet agent on linux: vagrant up agent
    To deploy and setup puppet agent on windows 2008: vagrant up winagent
